---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Portal Klien Terbatas | Epigrap">
  <div class="dashboard-placeholder">
    <div class="container message-box">
      <div class="lock-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
          <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
          <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1>Akses Terbatas</h1>
      <p>Halaman Dasbor/Portal Klien saat ini sedang dalam fase pengembangan infrastruktur backend terdesentralisasi (Sanity CMS & Clerk Auth).</p>
      <p>Akses log-in baru akan didistribusikan melalui undangan eksklusif secara langsung kepada Klien yang sudah menyelesaikan tahap reservasi fisik.</p>
      <a href="/" class="btn-outline-gold mt-4">Kembali ke Beranda</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .dashboard-placeholder {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(20, 20, 20, 1) 0%, rgba(5, 5, 5, 1) 100%);
    padding: 6rem 1rem;
  }

  .message-box {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    background: #0A0A0A;
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
  }

  .lock-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    color: var(--color-velvet);
  }
  
  .lock-icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-brass);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  p {
    color: #999;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mt-4 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-outline-gold {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--color-brass);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-brass);
    padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .btn-outline-gold:hover {
    background-color: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
